Please first consult the wiki page for guidance on the challenge and resources in the Hyperledger community. https://wiki.hyperledger.org/display/events/Global+CBDC+Challenge

Welcome to this chat channel where anyone who is working on the Global CBDC Challenge can share, coordinate, ask for help! Please first consult the wiki page for guidance on the challenge and resources in the Hyperledger community. https://wiki.hyperledger.org/display/events/Global+CBDC+Challenge

All Hyperledger Projects and Community Groups can be found in Chat as well (click on globe in top left to explore) and you can ask the community questions related to whatever project you're using. Some recommended channels to use are: #besu #fabric-questions #iroha #indy #capital-markets-sig #learning-materials-development-wg #identity-wg #public-sector-sig
